verses.text:
I have found the Pearl of greatest val-ue, Lost the dear joy for which I'd paid the cost;
I have found the Pearl of greatest val-ue, Nothing but good can-not be lost;
I have found the Pearl of great-est val-ue, Peace and joy, My all in all.

I have found my rest in Je-sus on-ly, I hold my sure-ty,
I have found my rest in Je-sus on-ly, Sav-ior, I love and trust and stay;
I have found my rest in Je-sus on-ly, Let me talk as sav-ior-ly.
